not sensitive to particle Lorentz boost), behaving like a set of three
scalars. This reduced model does not necessarily jeopardize the CPT
conservation, which depends truly on the character of the fixed vector
: there will occur conservation if one works with a purely space-like
external vector () , or breakdown, if 
